<title>btfhmny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 btfhmny wtḥs by tsmʿ klạmy ạlly mạbqwlhwsẖ
 wtḥbny tsẖfq ʿly wạ̉ṣgẖr nwr fy mạbtṭfyhwsẖ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉nạ ly myn yạ yswʿ gẖyr qlbk ạlly ḥbny
